description:
Dear Listeners,

We love you all so much and want to wish everyone Happy Holidays (or Happy Christmas as Anna likes to say)!

This holiday season we wanted to give you something special, so, we have compiled some of Unqualified’s most memorable moments from 2018 – please enjoy!

Love, Anna, Sim, and the entire Unqualified team

  • DAX SHEPARD discusses sex, parenting, and clickbait with Anna (1:26)
  • KELLY RIPA talks aging, porn, and Kegels (13:40)
  • JIMMY KIMMEL & MOLLY McNEARNEY play ‘Molly’s Game’ (19:40)
  • NICK JONAS reveals what he looks for in a woman (29:25)
  • JUDD APATPOW talks Stormy Daniels, Seth Rogen, & casting calls (30:55)
  • MAYIM BIALIK reads Dr. Seuss, talks co-parenting & gender roles (32:38)
  • ZACH BRAFF workshops Anna’s new podcast idea, “Bros Before Hoes” (48:53)
  • NATASHA LEGGERO & MOSHE KASHER explore ‘Mommy Issues’ & other Deal-Breakers (52:16)
  • KEVIN SMITH relives his heart attack experience (72:28)
  • EUGENIO DERBEZ helps Sim learn “Spanish” (85:04)
  • COLIN HANKS plays House Bunny Trivia with Anna (88:11)
  • BO BURNHAM and Anna help a caller struggling with the age gap between her and her boyfriend (96:15)
  • ALLISON JANNEY gets interviewed by ‘Cherry’ on the red-carpet (116:02) then performs a duet of “Take Me Back to Manhattan” with Anna (122:28)!

Check back on Tuesday for Part 2 of Unqualified’s Memorable Moments from 2018!!

 

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified
